(This is a backup script that takes all its params from a YAML file.)

This is a script to backup your assets/CMS folder and copy of your SQL database 
to a remote server and keep specifed number of copies (defined in the YAML file).
You can also use to sync all backups to your local or restore a bacup from the local 
or from server.

It creates a backup on your local machine and keeps a copy on the remote server.
It uses rsync to keep the backups synced.


Hope it helps anyone writing rake tasks or backup tasks. To learn few tips and tricks. ;)